metadata.name: DIURNAL
metadata.description:
On the foundation, these remarkable, technologically advanced pyramid like monuments, shoot rays of light energy into the sky every 24 hours. I don't know why this happens and where these rays go, but I know that they have something to do with the planets core; they're radioactive.

Zenith Prime is the new foundation, if life is to start here, it is my duty to make sure this planet is in no danger.
